LibreOffice just works for text, not too complicated spreadsheets and presentations, Teams, Outlook and the agenda work fine in the Chromium browser.
Sure, MS stopped supporting the Teams version for Linux but the web version works fine.<br>
Yes the companies pay</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64231622">

