		<div id="comment_body_64232274"><p>A consultant would implement a cloud solution, not recommend it. We're very careful about letting people know what their options are and letting <b>them</b> pick their poison.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64232274">

