	<div class="comment_share sharethis-0 hide"><span class="au"></span>
		<a class="t slashpop" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text="The Cloud" is just a remote server you don't own.%20by%20cirby%20%40slashdot%20https://it.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23222902&cid=64231790" target="_blank">twitter</a>
